commit bcdaea0
Author: Jure Varlec <jure.varlec@gmail.com>
Date:   Tue Feb 16 23:26:50 2010 +0100

    Fix the ipcmk issue.
    
    Done by not using ipcmk. It turns out that ipcmk uses time() to
    seed srandom(). Use /dev/urandom instead.
